    <briefdescription>
<para>SoC and Board hooks. </para>
    </briefdescription>
    <detaileddescription>
<para>This header file contains function prototypes for the interfaces between Zephyr&apos;s architecture and initialization code and SoC/board-specific logic that resides under boards/ and soc/</para>
<para><simplesect kind="note"><para>These are all standard SoC and board interfaces that are exported from SoC/board-specific logic to OS internal logic. These should never be accessed directly from application code but may be freely used within the OS. </para>
</simplesect>
</para>
